{"tid":2512879,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：本月落實非公務員僱員簽聲明　首長級赴內地研習比例擬升至100%","createTime":"2021-05-02T05:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T05:43:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd6ff2ef6c8f882ce80153f05ec81d91bea5209a","tid":2512879,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:43:10.000Z","msg":"政務司長張建宗今（2日）發網誌表示，政府計劃在本月落實並公布將簽署聲明擁護《基本法》、效忠香港特區的要求延伸到按非公務員條款聘任的政府僱員。另外，張建宗稱公務員培訓處為中高級及首長級人員提供參加內地國家事務研習課程的名額由2015年的640個增至2019年的1000個，政府希望把首長級人員到內地參加研習課程的比例由目前約75%逐步提升至100%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210502/s00001/1619929551061/%e5%bc%b5%e5%bb%ba%e5%ae%97-%e6%9c%ac%e6%9c%88%e8%90%bd%e5%af%a6%e9%9d%9e%e5%85%ac%e5%8b%99%e5%93%a1%e5%83%b1%e5%93%a1%e7%b0%bd%e8%81%b2%e6%98%8e-%e9%a6%96%e9%95%b7%e7%b4%9a%e8%b5%b4%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e7%a0%94%e7%bf%92%e6%af%94%e4%be%8b%e6%93%ac%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b3100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210502%2Fs00001%2F1619929551061%2F%25e5%25bc%25b5%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e5%25ae%2597-%25e6%259c%25ac%25e6%259c%2588%25e8%2590%25bd%25e5%25af%25a6%25e9%259d%259e%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%2583%25b1%25e5%2593%25a1%25e7%25b0%25bd%25e8%2581%25b2%25e6%2598%258e-%25e9%25a6%2596%25e9%2595%25b7%25e7%25b4%259a%25e8%25b5%25b4%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%259c%25b0%25e7%25a0%2594%25e7%25bf%2592%25e6%25af%2594%25e4%25be%258b%25e6%2593%25ac%25e5%258d%2587%25e8%2587%25b3100&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNmdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=736324c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210502%2Fs00001%2F1619929551061%2F%25e5%25bc%25b5%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e5%25ae%2597-%25e6%259c%25ac%25e6%259c%2588%25e8%2590%25bd%25e5%25af%25a6%25e9%259d%259e%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%2583%25b1%25e5%2593%25a1%25e7%25b0%25bd%25e8%2581%25b2%25e6%259